msgctxt "an6.110:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.110:0.2"
msgid "11. Tikavagga "
msgstr "11. Triads "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.110:0.3"
msgid "110. Saññāsutta "
msgstr "110. Perceptions "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.447, sc1
msgctxt "an6.110:1.1"
msgid "“Tayome, bhikkhave, dhammā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these three things. "

msgctxt "an6.110:1.2"
msgid "Katame tayo? "
msgstr "What three? "

msgctxt "an6.110:1.3"
msgid "Kāmasaññā, byāpādasaññā, vihiṃsāsaññā. "
msgstr "Sensual, malicious, and cruel perceptions. "

msgctxt "an6.110:1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo dhammā. "
msgstr "These are the three things. "

msgctxt "an6.110:1.5"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tiṇṇaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya tayo dhammā bhāvetabbā. "
msgstr "To give up these three things you should develop three things. "

msgctxt "an6.110:1.6"
msgid "Katame tayo? "
msgstr "What three? "

msgctxt "an6.110:1.7"
msgid "Kāmasaññāya pahānāya nekkhammasaññā bhāvetabbā, byāpādasaññāya pahānāya abyāpādasaññā bhāvetabbā, vihiṃsāsaññāya pahānāya avihiṃsāsaññā bhāvetabbā. "
msgstr "You should develop perceptions of renunciation to give up sensual perceptions, perceptions of good will to give up malicious perceptions, and perceptions of harmlessness to give up cruel perceptions. "

msgctxt "an6.110:1.8"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tiṇṇaṃ dhammānaṃ pahānāya ime tayo dhammā bhāvetabbā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the three things you should develop to give up those three things.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.110:1.9"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

